    "content": "# Architecture\n\nZYX architecture is designed for high performance, scalability, and ACID compliance.\n\n## Core Architecture\n\n- [Overview](overview) - System architecture overview\n- [Storage System](storage) - Segment-based storage engine\n- [Query Engine](query-engine) - Query execution pipeline\n- [Transaction System](transactions) - ACID transaction implementation\n\n## Storage Details\n\n- [Segment Format](segment-format) - On-disk storage format\n- [WAL Implementation](wal) - Write-ahead logging\n- [Cache Management](cache) - Caching strategies\n\n## Performance\n\n- [Optimization Strategies](optimization) - Performance tuning\n- [Benchmarks](benchmarks) - Performance metrics",
