    "projectOrder": 1,
    "content": "# Development Setup\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- C++20 compiler\n- Meson, Conan, Ninja\n- Google Test\n- ANTLR4 (for parser changes)\n\n## Building\n\n```bash\nconan install . --output-folder=buildDir --build=missing\nmeson setup buildDir\nmeson compile -C buildDir\n```\n\n## Testing\n\n```bash\n./scripts/run_tests.sh\n```",
